{"tid":1763890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 抗爭係進入樽頸 但唔係轉向政府一邊，唔好妄自菲薄","createTime":"2019-11-30T16:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T17:05:41.000Z","uid":81236,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9844b33b2835d1cd3f982bfba5c06f8d94585e","tid":1763890,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"相信大家都見到數據<br />\n<br />\n對於要求成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n及解散警隊嘅支持度都有少少下降<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但</span><br />\n<br />\n大家考慮少咗區選呢個因素影響<br />\n<br />\n我相信唔少和理非同政府官都視區選為一個民意出口<br />\n<br />\n希望藉住區選當比香港人發洩左就算<br />\n<br />\n如果經考慮後<br />\n<br />\n減少嘅民意百分比有5%左右<br />\n<br />\n就極有可能係由中立轉淺黃既人仕<br />\n覺得經區選後應該問題已經解決<br />\n<br />\n但減少左嘅百分比係好值得留意同絕對係一個警號<br />\n<br />\n如何減低香港人三分鐘熱度<br />\n<br />\n保持對爭取民主自由既耐性同決心<br />\n<br />\n將五大訴求既好處再推廣轉化為民意<br />\n<br />\n以及全面抗爭，不可再只依賴勇武抗爭<br />\n<br />\n係香港人要好好考慮<br />\n<br />\n唔好再重蹈2014既覆轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會對唔住幾千位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5564dfe0426e76a6eaed577789a9c58739ee119b","tid":1763890,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdba1ef3a52e220162884ca7d3a28f3b0c1e3845","tid":1763890,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec382bbd9e195aa17215d81bac34cbdaab45b3d3","tid":1763890,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"大家反而要小心墮入自我實現圈套<br />\n<br />\n政府發出信息反對人數減少<br />\n&mdash;&gt;<br />\n覺得少咗人所以唔反抗及遊行等等<br />\n&mdash;&gt;<br />\n結果少咗人出嚟行<br />\n&mdash;&gt;<br />\n政府話反對人數減少<br />\n<br />\n呢個係大個循環"},{"pid":"f57fb889db8300c698b177f43279274fae0d1e51","tid":1763890,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"另外希望咁多位香港人明白<br />\n<br />\n香港人日後唔會再有可能有另一次實現真普選嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n輸咗今次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係一世<br />\n同埋我哋嘅下一代"},{"pid":"3edc74e00f3f7da91d254c3a201342c3a2d82cdc","tid":1763890,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"用任何方法再次點起抗爭嘅火炎，勝利只會屬於堅持到底個一方"},{"pid":"b0cdbc850c2190bb4ed6d179cd7a7afe9b7b64a3","tid":1763890,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"我見到有個poly學生都反對佔校<br />\n可能逆轉咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/rFdynXh.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFdynXh.jpg&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b7af309b\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/rFdynXh.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmjhPCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmjhPCi.png&h=1e44f8d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dcc3f821dbcc47fa23e62f4512a7025ddb3dfd6","tid":1763890,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"「請幫推」舉行民間放映會，播返黑警啲罪證，唔好比場運動降溫。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1763894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1763894</a><br />\n幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f3deeed46181388d242a61017bf0d14cfb8d6f","tid":1763890,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dcc3f821dbcc47fa23e62f4512a7025ddb3dfd6","tid":1763890,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"「請幫推」舉行民間放映會，播返黑警啲罪證，唔好比場運動降溫。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1763894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1763894</a><br />\n幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"我提議搞返放映會，唔好降溫<br />\n不如幫我推下<img src=